I saw Holy Grail was about to expire on Netflix and submitted “watch 20 minutes, if you hate it we’ll vote again on what to watch”
Knowing this generation doesn’t have the greatest attention span I expected to be shut down before we even hit 10 minutes. They watched they entire thing, even asking to rewind scenes. I even geeked out and busted some trivia after.
I can die happy. Now my watch has ended.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/3JUTQn4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GrandChampion]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What else would we need?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NmyBJTN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oUDD9lc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NmyBJTN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vladrichdemaclant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>they are really good friends</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CdPcDhI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NlvnyFK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CdPcDhI</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AbletBlowPop]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Noted.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wE9coFv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/61agM7Q.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Noted.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wE9coFv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[RoseBeef]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cat is having the best sleep of his life</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/x8U1w0e</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LnAkv3k.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/x8U1w0e</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Woultsedommere]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>At all costs</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CsOmE9b</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/U1gcJH2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CsOmE9b</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LordoftheHildago]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Well executed.</title><link>http